    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo defines how to store in the Internet Domain Name System the mapping information needed by e-mail gateways and other tools to map RFC822 domain names into X.400 O/R names and vice versa.  This memo defines an Experimental Protocol for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
